Interface JobRequest.JobScheduledCallback

  • Enclosing class:
    JobRequest

    public static interface JobRequest.JobScheduledCallback
    Callback that is used when scheduling a JobRequest asynchronously on a background thread.

    • Method Detail

      • onJobScheduled

        void onJobScheduled(int jobId,
                    @NonNull
                    String tag,
                    @Nullable
                    Exception exception)
        Called after your request was scheduled.
        Parameters:
        jobId - The unique ID of your new scheduled JobRequest. Or JOB_ID_ERROR in case of a failure.
        tag - The tag of the scheduled request.
        exception - If scheduling the request failed, then the exception won't be null.
